text: Fernand Ravoux (8 April 1876 - 15 November 1950) was a French gymnast. He competed in the men's individual all-around event at the 1900 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1876 births Category:1950 deaths Category:French male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of France Category:Gymnasts at the 1900 Summer Olympics Category:People from Cambrai
